YR. HGT. P None 04,16,05,06,04 TOP RETURNERS YR. HGT. P Heather Hollis Sr. 6-0 
C Kate Turnbull Jr. 5-10 F 04,17,05,06,04 TOP NEWCOMERS YR. HGT. P Emily Ela 
