Prince Charlie is fit to be king: "Only as an Elvis impersonator." 
</P>
<P>
 Reader Steve Due of Inglewood has a plan that guarantees no city would ever 
attempt to take the L.A. Rams out of Southern California: "Force any bidder to 
make it a package deal with the Clippers." 
</P>
