<P>
 The Los Angeles City Council today is scheduled to consider Mayor Richard 
Riordan's proposal to set up a sister city relationship with Ho Chi Minh City, 
formerly Saigon. 
</P>
<P>
 Some Vietnam veterans groups have called the move premature, saying the 
