 Occupants of the van had shot at officers on Chicago's North Side, police 
said. Officers then chased the van south on the Kennedy Expressway. The fleeing 
van crossed into opposing traffic and continued south in the northbound lanes 
for about a mile before colliding with the car, police said. Two of the dead 
