<HEADLINE>
<P>
SPOTLIGHT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Coach Jim Barnett's teams, Trabuco Hills and Long Beach Poly, are 6-0 against 
Long Beach Jordan. 
</P>
<P>
 * Newport Harbor sets a school record with 12th football victory. 
</P>
<P>
 * When did county's No. 1 and No. 2 football teams last meet? 
</P>
<P>
 * Last season, when No. 1 Los Alamitos beat Huntington Beach, 39-21, for 
Division II title. 
