 * Ralphs. $5 increments, $5-$25. 
</P>
<P>
 * Lucky. 50 and up. (Limit on cash back.) Call (800) 83-LUCKY to order 
certificates by phone. Prorated discount certificates start at $500 and max out 
at $5,000. 
